Revision history for Perl module OAuth::Consumer

0.03 2013-03-12

 - Better error checking in get_access_token
 - Small addition in the documentation
 - Better handling of the oauth verifier
 - Removed some tests because the service is down
 - Better error reporting for remote server errors

0.02 2013-02-21

 - Remove the requirement of a Perl with threads
 - Add the 'thread' mode for getting a verifier

0.01 2013-02-18

 - Initial release
